      <title>英国将在不当销售投诉后审查汽车贷款佣金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/uk-to-review-car-loan-commissions-after-misselling-complaints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国金融行为监管局表示，将审查 2021 年之前发放的汽车金融贷款，此举可能导致数百万客户有资格获得赔偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/uk-to-review-car-loan-commissions-after-misselling-complaints</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:23:27 GMT</pubDate>
